    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110200/extras/fc4d1bd7e8775729cbbaffe1d8526719.avif?t=1734917701\" width=614 height=166 /></span><br><br><strong><u>A thrilling challenge that starts with a simple click!</u></strong><br><br>Keep It UP is a rock climbing puzzle-action game that you can enjoy with simple controls. Conquer the summit with your own strategy on climbing courses full of various gimmicks and obstacles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110200/extras/cfef79f9d5fe84489c18eabdf47de729.poster.avif?t=1734917701\" width=382 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110200/extras/cfef79f9d5fe84489c18eabdf47de729.webm?t=1734917701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110200/extras/cfef79f9d5fe84489c18eabdf47de729.mp4?t=1734917701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▶Intuitive click controls</strong><br>Create your own climbing route by selecting holders within the circular area around the player.<br><strong>▶Strategic gameplay</strong><br>Overcome difficulties by making the best choices for each situation.<br><strong>▶Challenge and growth</strong><br>Feel your skills improve as you progress through the game.<br><strong>▶Importance of rest</strong><br>You'll understand the meaning of 'more haste, less speed'.<br><br>A challenging journey awaits you. Don't give up and keep pushing towards the summit!",
